&lt;img width="1258" height="1688" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e8d59ed5-b00f-49b0-b7bb-3ace063f5c8d" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1262" height="1684" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f0d02b23-224a-4d3b-9296-774d6dd9cdff" /&gt;
